OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny intervals with patchy
OL,6,Fcloud and a few showers in the
OL,7,Fmorning, mainly affecting Shetland,
OL,8,Fthese starting to die out to leave a
OL,9,Fdry afternoon with long spells of
OL,10,Fsunshine. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and clear evening
OL,13,Fleading into a chilly night, but
OL,14,Fclouding over towards dawn, with a few
OL,15,Fshowers moving towards Shetland,
OL,16,Ffreshening southerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
