OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with strengthening
OL,6,Fsoutherly winds, some light outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain in the morning before further
OL,8,Frain in the afternoon but some drier
OL,9,Fconditions too.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA wet
OL,12,Fstart to the new week but rain
OL,13,Fclearing later on Monday, some settled
OL,14,Fconditions on Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,15,Fwith some March sunshine breaking
OL,16,Fthrough.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
